ecurity/sanctions/Pages/sanctions.aspx','Fazl Mohammad Mazloom','2018-12-31 03:11:34','2018-12-31 03:11:34'),('au-dfat-sanctions.24','au-dfat-sanctions','individual','Title: Mullah. Designation: Deputy, Minister of Defence under the Taliban regime. Arrested in Feb. 2010 and in custody in Pakistan. Extradition request to Afghanistan pending in Lahore High Court, Pakistan as of June 2011. Belongs to Popalzai tribe. Senior Taliban military commander and member of Taliban Quetta Council as of May 2007. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 1 Jun. 2010.','1988 (Taliban)','http://dfat.gov.au/international-relations/security/sanctions/Pages/sanctions.aspx','Abdul Ghani Baradar Abdul Ahmad Turk','2018-12-31 03:11:34','2018-12-31 03:11:34'),('au-dfat-sanctions.24','au-dfat-sanctions','individual','Title: Mullah. Designation: Deputy, Minister of Defence under the Taliban regime. Arrested in Feb. 2010 and in custody in Pakistan. Extradition request to Afghanistan pending in Lahore High Court, Pakistan as of June 2011. Belongs to Popalzai tribe. Senior Taliban military commander and member of Taliban Quetta Council as of May 2007. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 1 Jun. 2010.','1988 (Taliban)','http://dfat.gov.au/international-relations/security/sanctions/Pages/sanctions.aspx','Abdul Ghani Baradar Abdul Ahmad Turk','2018-12-31 03:11:34','2018-12-31 03:11:34'),('au-dfat-sanctions.25','au-dfat-sanctions','individual','Title: Mullah. Designation: Commander of Central Corps under the Taliban regime. Member of the Taliban Quetta Shura as at 2009. Taliban member responsible for Uruzgan Province, Afghanistan, as at 2011. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 1 Jun. 2010. ','1988 (Taliban)','http://dfat.gov.au/international-relations/security/sanctions/Pages/sanctions.aspx','Abdul Rauf Khadem','2018-12-31 03:11:34','2018-12-31 03:11:34'),('au-dfat-sanctions.26','au-dfa